
External libs required
----------------------

To compile Mtp Target, you needs followings libraries : 

- libxml2 (libxml2-dev)
- freetype (libfreetype6-dev)
- openGL 1.2 (mesag3+ggi-dev)
- STLport 4.5 (libstlport4.5-dev)
- lua (liblua50-dev)

On Debian you can easily get package : apt-get install <module name>
You will need some other library : 
- NeL : see http://www.nevrax.org for more information
- fmod (optionnal) : http://www.fmod.org/
- ODE 0.05(not the cvs version) : http://ode.org/
- Lua script engine : http://www.lua.org/

* Edit Variables.mk to change external library paths and includes

* make update

* make 

* Dynamic libraries needs to be in LD_LIBRARY_PATH variable :
  export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$(HOME)/external/nel/lib

